column10: Mini Project: Report on Steps Insights on Data Cleaning and Analysis Task
Click on "Data" from the menu bar
click on "Remove duplicate" on the on the data tool group
Highlights the first row that contains "inf" by clicking on the row number
Hold down control key and click on all the row numbers of the remaining rows containing "inf"
Right click and select "delete rows" from the list of actions
First of all sort the entire data by Region
Insert rows at the end of each region to provide space for totals per region
Calculate the total quantity and value for each region
List regions, quantities and prices per Unit respectively
Calculate the totals using the SUM function
Highlight the summary data and go to "Insert" on the the menu bar
